result.purpose: Defines various data models related to application management, including versioning, operator interactions, history tracking, mandatory updates, and notifications.
result.architecture: The folder follows a modular architecture pattern, where each file defines a specific entity model used for managing different aspects of the application.

internal/domains/manager/models/app_vers.purpose: Defines the VersionEntity model for managing application version data.

internal/domains/manager/models/auth.go.purpose: Defines the OperatorEntity model for database interactions.

internal/domains/manager/models/generic..purpose: Defines the HistoryEntity model for tracking changes in an application.

internal/domains/manager/models/mandator.purpose: Defines the MandatoryUpdateEntity model for database interactions.

internal/domains/manager/models/noti.go.purpose: Defines data models for notifications in the application.
